---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout title="Posting Guidelines - VapeIndex">
  <Header />

  <main class="main-content">
    <div class="content-container">
      <div class="page-header">
        <h1>‚úçÔ∏è Posting Guidelines</h1>
        <p>How to create quality posts and contribute to the community</p>
      </div>

      <div class="guidelines-grid">
        <div class="guideline-card">
          <div class="icon">üìù</div>
          <h2>Write Clear Titles</h2>
          <p>Use descriptive, specific titles that clearly explain what your post is about. Avoid clickbait or vague titles.</p>
          <div class="examples">
            <div class="example good">
              <strong>‚úÖ Good:</strong> "Elf Bar BC5000 vs Lost Mary BM5000 - Flavor Comparison"
            </div>
            <div class="example bad">
              <strong>‚ùå Bad:</strong> "Which one is better?"
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="guideline-card">
          <div class="icon">üéØ</div>
          <h2>Choose the Right Board</h2>
          <p>Post in the board that best matches your topic. This helps users find relevant content.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>/b/disposables</strong> - Disposable vape discussions</li>
            <li><strong>/b/pods</strong> - Pod systems and refillable devices</li>
            <li><strong>/b/beginner</strong> - Questions from newcomers</li>
            <li><strong>/b/diy</strong> - DIY e-liquid and coil building</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="guideline-card">
          <div class="icon">üîç</div>
          <h2>Search Before Posting</h2>
          <p>Before asking a question, search to see if it's been answered. This reduces duplicate posts and helps you find answers faster.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="guideline-card">
          <div class="icon">üì∏</div>
          <h2>Include Photos When Helpful</h2>
          <p>For questions about devices, authenticity checks, or build showcases, include clear photos to help others assist you.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="guideline-card">
          <div class="icon">üí¨</div>
          <h2>Be Constructive</h2>
          <p>Provide helpful comments. If you disagree, explain why respectfully. Share your experience and knowledge.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="guideline-card">
          <div class="icon">‚ö†Ô∏è</div>
          <h2>Safety First</h2>
          <p>When discussing battery safety, nicotine handling, or health topics, prioritize accurate information. Lives may depend on it.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="guideline-card">
          <div class="icon">üè∑Ô∏è</div>
          <h2>Use Tags Appropriately</h2>
          <p>Tag posts accurately (Question, Review, Discussion, etc.) to help users filter content.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="guideline-card">
          <div class="icon">üö´</div>
          <h2>What Not to Post</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Personal information (yours or others')</li>
            <li>Links to fake/counterfeit products</li>
            <li>Promotional content or spam</li>
            <li>Off-topic content unrelated to vaping</li>
            <li>Medical advice (suggest seeing professionals)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tips-box">
        <h3>üí° Pro Tips for Great Posts</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide context - mention your experience level, current device, preferences</li>
          <li>Be specific about your budget when asking for recommendations</li>
          <li>Update your post if you solve your own problem (helps others!)</li>
          <li>Thank people who help you - it encourages more participation</li>
          <li>Upvote helpful comments and posts</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .content-container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .page-header {
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
    padding: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .page-header p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .guidelines-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .guideline-card {
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
    border-radius: 0;
    padding: 0.75rem;
  }

  .icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .guideline-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .guideline-card p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .guideline-card ul {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }

  .guideline-card li {
    margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
  }

  .examples {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .example {
    padding: 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .example.good {
    background: #D1FAE5;
    border: 1px solid #10B981;
    color: #065F46;
  }

  .example.bad {
    background: #FEE2E2;
    border: 1px solid #EF4444;
    color: #991B1B;
  }

  .tips-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand) 0%, #EC4899 100%);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 0;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .tips-box h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .tips-box ul {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .tips-box li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .content-container {
      padding: 0.5rem;
      margin: 1rem auto;
    }

    .page-header {
      padding: 0.75rem;
    }

    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }

    .guidelines-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .guideline-card {
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
